
## ‚úÖ POST TEST 10.7 ‚Äì JAWABAN LENGKAP

### üìå Soal:

Tambahkan skenario program login dengan perilaku:

1. **Fitur pendaftaran user baru** (email, no telp, nama, username, password)
2. **Simpan data user ke database**
3. **Terapkan exception handling pada form pendaftaran**

---

## 1Ô∏è‚É£ Fitur Pendaftaran User Baru

### üìñ Penjelasan

Program ditambahkan **form registrasi** menggunakan Java Swing yang berisi:

* Nama
* Email
* No. Telepon
* Username
* Password
* Tombol **Register**

Form ini memungkinkan user baru mendaftar sebelum login.

---

### üíª Contoh Kode (Form Register)

```java
import javax.swing.*;
import java.awt.event.*;

public class RegisterForm extends JFrame implements ActionListener {

    JTextField txtNama, txtEmail, txtTelp, txtUsername;
    JPasswordField txtPassword;
    JButton btnRegister;

    public RegisterForm() {
        setTitle("Register User");
        setSize(350, 300);
        setLayout(null);
        setDefaultCloseOperation(EXIT_ON_CLOSE);

        JLabel l1 = new JLabel("Nama");
        l1.setBounds(20, 20, 100, 25);
        add(l1);

        txtNama = new JTextField();
        txtNama.setBounds(120, 20, 180, 25);
        add(txtNama);

        JLabel l2 = new JLabel("Email");
        l2.setBounds(20, 55, 100, 25);
        add(l2);

        txtEmail = new JTextField();
        txtEmail.setBounds(120, 55, 180, 25);
        add(txtEmail);

        JLabel l3 = new JLabel("No Telp");
        l3.setBounds(20, 90, 100, 25);
        add(l3);

        txtTelp = new JTextField();
        txtTelp.setBounds(120, 90, 180, 25);
        add(txtTelp);

        JLabel l4 = new JLabel("Username");
        l4.setBounds(20, 125, 100, 25);
        add(l4);

        txtUsername = new JTextField();
        txtUsername.setBounds(120, 125, 180, 25);
        add(txtUsername);

        JLabel l5 = new JLabel("Password");
        l5.setBounds(20, 160, 100, 25);
        add(l5);

        txtPassword = new JPasswordField();
        txtPassword.setBounds(120, 160, 180, 25);
        add(txtPassword);

        btnRegister = new JButton("Register");
        btnRegister.setBounds(120, 200, 100, 30);
        btnRegister.addActionListener(this);
        add(btnRegister);

        setVisible(true);
    }

    @Override
    public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
        // diproses di bagian database
    }

    public static void main(String[] args) {
        new RegisterForm();
    }
}
```

---

## 2Ô∏è‚É£ Menyimpan Data User ke Database

### üìñ Penjelasan

* Database menggunakan **SQLite**
* Data disimpan ke tabel `users`
* Proses insert menggunakan **PreparedStatement** (aman dari SQL Injection)

---

### üóÑÔ∏è Struktur Tabel Database

```sql
CREATE TABLE users (
    id INTEGER PRIMARY KEY AUTOINCREMENT,
    nama TEXT,
    email TEXT,
    telp TEXT,
    username TEXT,
    password TEXT
);
```

---

### üíª Kode Simpan ke Database

```java
import java.sql.*;

public class DatabaseConnection {

    public static Connection getConnection() throws Exception {
        String url = "jdbc:sqlite:users.db";
        return DriverManager.getConnection(url);
    }
}
```

Tambahkan pada `actionPerformed` di `RegisterForm`:

```java
@Override
public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
    try {
        Connection conn = DatabaseConnection.getConnection();

        String sql = "INSERT INTO users (nama, email, telp, username, password) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)";
        PreparedStatement pst = conn.prepareStatement(sql);

        pst.setString(1, txtNama.getText());
        pst.setString(2, txtEmail.getText());
        pst.setString(3, txtTelp.getText());
        pst.setString(4, txtUsername.getText());
        pst.setString(5, new String(txtPassword.getPassword()));

        pst.executeUpdate();
        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(this, "Registrasi berhasil");

        conn.close();

    } catch (Exception ex) {
        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(this, ex.getMessage());
    }
}
```

---

## 3Ô∏è‚É£ Exception Handling pada Form Pendaftaran

### üìñ Penjelasan

Exception handling digunakan untuk:

* Data kosong
* Gagal koneksi database
* Kesalahan input user

---

### üíª Class Exception Khusus

```java
class RegisterException extends Exception {
    public RegisterException(String message) {
        super(message);
    }
}
```

---

### üíª Implementasi Exception Handling

```java
@Override
public void actionPerformed(ActionEvent e) {
    try {
        if (txtNama.getText().isEmpty() ||
            txtEmail.getText().isEmpty() ||
            txtTelp.getText().isEmpty() ||
            txtUsername.getText().isEmpty() ||
            txtPassword.getPassword().length == 0) {

            throw new RegisterException("Semua field harus diisi!");
        }

        Connection conn = DatabaseConnection.getConnection();
        String sql = "INSERT INTO users (nama, email, telp, username, password) VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?)";
        PreparedStatement pst = conn.prepareStatement(sql);

        pst.setString(1, txtNama.getText());
        pst.setString(2, txtEmail.getText());
        pst.setString(3, txtTelp.getText());
        pst.setString(4, txtUsername.getText());
        pst.setString(5, new String(txtPassword.getPassword()));

        pst.executeUpdate();
        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(this, "Registrasi berhasil");
        conn.close();

    } catch (RegisterException ex) {
        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(this, ex.getMessage());
    } catch (Exception ex) {
        JOptionPane.showMessageDialog(this, "Error: " + ex.getMessage());
    }
}

Tinggal bilang mau format apa üëç
